safetyTips: Restricting number of customers in shop. Home delivery consignments packaged in a "non-public" environment, a dedicated facility. Our courier is DPD who practise contactless delivery.
name: Moxon's Fishmongers
description: We are a high street retail fishmonger specialising in the finest British fish and shellfish. We also produce our own range of smoked fish and ready to eat foods and have an extensive selection of deli items and store cupboard goods. You can now order online for next day home delivery anywhere in the UK.
